Business Brief -- Hoechst AG:
   Unit Sues Allied-Signal Inc.,
   Alleging Patent Infringement
A spokesman for Allied-Signal said the Morristown, N.J.,
company had been aware of Hoechst's concerns prior to the
suit's filing and had determined that neither its
manufacturing process nor the product infringes on Hoechst's
patents. He said Allied-Signal intends to "vigorously defend"
itself against the suit.